    "description": "🌟 COMPLETE API COLLECTION FOR SARASWATI CLASSES BACKEND\n\n📚 Base URL Configuration:\n- Development: http://localhost:3000\n- Production: Your production URL\n\n🔑 Authentication:\n- Auto-saves tokens from login responses\n- Supports both Admin and Student roles\n- JWT Bearer Token authentication\n\n📊 What's Included:\n✅ Health & System Check\n✅ Authentication (Login, Register, Logout, Profile)\n✅ Public Content APIs (Courses, Test Series, Blogs, etc.)\n✅ Complete Student Dashboard\n✅ Complete Admin Management\n✅ Course & Test Series Management\n✅ Enrollment Processing\n✅ Content Management (Blogs, Resources, Gallery, Results)\n✅ Banner & Feature Flag Management\n✅ File Upload (Images & Documents)\n✅ Notifications System\n✅ Contact & Inquiry Forms\n✅ Analytics Dashboard\n\n🎯 Total Endpoints: 150+\n📝 Total Requests: 150+\n\n👨‍💻 Perfect for:\n- API Testing & Development\n- QA & Regression Testing\n- Documentation Reference\n- Team Onboarding\n- Client Demonstrations"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// 🚀 Auto-save tokens from login responses",
          "if (pm.response.code === 200 && pm.request.method === 'POST' && pm.request.url.path.includes('/auth/')) {",
          "    try {",
          "        const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
          "        if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.accessToken) {",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', jsonData.data.refreshToken);",
          "            console.log('✅ Tokens auto-saved successfully');",
          "        }",
          "    } catch (e) {",
          "        console.log('⚠️ Token auto-save skipped (not a login response)');",
          "    }",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
